org.sakaiproject.coursemanagement.api

Interface Meeting

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MeetingCmImpl

    public interface Meeting
    A time and a place for a Section to meet. Meetings are completely controlled by their sections. To add a Meeting to a Section, call section.getMeetings() and operate on the List of meetings.
    Author:
    Josh Holtzman
